Description:


When the new Babysitter, Jessica, arrives; Kimberly and Tony go out for a night on the town. Jessica invites her friends over for some fun and frolic while the couple is out. When the couple gets home early to discover the party instead of getting mad, they join in. What comes next is an evening that you'll never forget


This is a typical obvious, one-day factory porn.  The babysitter (James), her boyfriend (Blake Palmer, still being palmed off as a teenager!), and their friends fuck while the parents are away, and then fuck the parents.  Yawn.  Except for the lovely Stacey King in the opener, and the fair pair of badly-intercut closers matching Kummings and Palmer, and Tedeschi and James, total boredom
